---
title: Zesty Turkey One-Pot Chili  with Cheesy Tortilla Chips
description: This quick and zesty turkey chili, simmered with black beans, packs a major flavour punch in just 15 minutes. Enjoy it with crispy, cheesy tortilla chips for dipping.
